ainst certain types of mobs.  <br><br>We, with warriors, are the worst soloers of any class, so rogues have to be grouped to get decent exp.  But usually we're very welcome in groups, because of that damage output.  We're a very flexible class too.. you just have to play it right.<br><br>Jarkell Ravensteel<br>Dawn Rising <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ucpete2.showPublicProfile?language=EN>c pete2</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 239<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/17/02 10:28:19 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2159.topic&index=5>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: so, tell me about...</span><hr size=1> Cool, been reading up on them and found some pretty nifty info. seems you can hide and sneak at the same time, you just move slow. <br><br>i imagine a popular tactic is to let the main tank gain agro, step in for a backstab, evade, wait a sec and repeat? <p><center><i>...His Majesty: Pete Trismegistus,  God-King of all He sees....</i><center></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=d1c3b5><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub94.ezboard.com/upentapod.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Pentapod</A>&nbsp; <IMG HEIGHT=10 WIDTH=10 SRC="http://members.ozemail.com.au/~pentapod/graphics/a_pod.gif" BORDER=0></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>  Posts: 250<br> <font color=#A62A2A>(6/17/02 10:32:31 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub94.ezboard.com/ffirionaviefrm1.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=2159.topic&index=6>Reply</a>   <BR><img src=http://members.ozemail.com.au/~pentapod/miscpics/couple.jpg height=200 width=100.gif></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: so, tell me about...</span><hr size=1> The LoS does no